            html: `<p><a href="https://www.howtostudykorean.com/?page_id=502">Lesson 9</a>: In this lesson, you will learn how to conjugate 이다 which is conjugated differently than other verbs and adjectives. You will learn about how to conjugate 이다 in the four honorific formalities that you already know. In addition, you will learn how to use 이다 to conjugate verbs/adjectives to the future by creating endings like: 먹을 것이다.</p>`,
